best cow
Homonym Number:
Word Class: noun
Sense Number:  1
Definition:a tap outside the cowshed used by unscrupulous dairy farmers to ''water down'' the milk.


Origin: [none]
Register:
Register 2:
Flag: Farm Words
Domain: Rural
Region: [none]
